page.title: 10 HOUSES FOR SALE Cont.
page.content: Tenure:Freehold with vacant possession. Price : Offers invited of 85000 pounds. Accommodation. Ground Floor: Entrance Hall, Morning Room, Study, Dining Room,Breakfast Room, Kitchen, Cloakroom, Drawing Room. First Floor: Landing, 6 Bedrooms, Bathroom, Shower Room. Second Floor: Landing, 5 Bedroom, Bathroom, Washroom. Outside: Cellar, Lean-to Greenhouse, Walled Gardens. The property was formerly used as part of the Rockhampton Equitation School and was until recently let as self-catering flats producing a substantial income. It is sold with Planning permission for change of use to a Home for the Elderly. Estate Agents: King Miles. Sold June
